Class ResourceTemplate

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Identifiable<URI>>, Unique<URI>
public final class ResourceTemplate
extends Identifiable<URI>

A single "node" in a REST API's path-based Web resource model's hierarchical usage. Note: This is a metadata class - instances should be edited with tools and persisted for reuse.
